statements: SELECT symbol, date, price, volume FROM stock_prices WHERE symbol = 'AAPL';
SELECT * FROM stock_prices WHERE volume > 1000000;
SELECT symbol, price FROM stock_prices WHERE date >= '2022-01-01' ORDER BY price DESC;
SELECT symbol, date FROM stock_prices WHERE price < 50 ORDER BY date ASC;
SELECT AVG(price) AS average_price, MAX(price) AS max_price, MIN(price) AS min_price FROM stock_prices;
SELECT symbol, price FROM stock_prices WHERE volume > 100000 ORDER BY date DESC, price ASC;
SELECT * FROM stock_prices WHERE price > 50.00 AND date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-02-28';
SELECT symbol, MAX(price) as max_price FROM stock_prices GROUP BY symbol HAVING max_price > 100.00 ORDER BY max_price DESC;
SELECT AVG(price) as avg_price, COUNT(*) as total_records FROM stock_prices WHERE date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT symbol, SUM(volume) as total_volume FROM stock_prices GROUP BY symbol ORDER BY total_volume DESC LIMIT 3;
SELECT * FROM stock_prices;
SELECT date, stock_price FROM stock_prices WHERE stock_price > 100;
SELECT stock_id, date, stock_price FROM stock_prices ORDER BY date DESC;
SELECT stock_id, MAX(stock_price) FROM stock_prices GROUP BY stock_id;
SELECT strategy_id, stock_id, start_date, end_date FROM strategy_analysis WHERE strategy_id = 1;
SELECT stock_id, date, stock_price, volume FROM stock_prices WHERE stock_price > 100 ORDER BY date DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT * FROM stock_prices WHERE volume > 1000 AND stock_price BETWEEN 50 AND 100 ORDER BY stock_price ASC, date DESC;
SELECT stock_id, MIN(stock_price) AS min_price, MAX(stock_price) AS max_price FROM stock_prices GROUP BY stock_id HAVING COUNT(*) > 5;
SELECT stock_id, AVG(stock_price) AS avg_price, COUNT(*) AS price_count FROM stock_prices GROUP BY stock_id HAVING AVG(stock_price) > 75 ORDER BY avg_price DESC, price_count ASC;

SELECT sp.stock_id, sa.strategy_id, sp.date, sa.start_date, sa.end_date FROM stock_prices sp JOIN strategy_analysis sa ON sp.stock_id = sa.stock_id WHERE sp.date >= sa.start_date AND sp.date <= sa.end_date ORDER BY sp.stock_id ASC, sa.strategy_id DESC;

SELECT symbol, price, volume FROM stock_prices WHERE price < 50 ORDER BY volume DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT symbol, date, price FROM stock_prices WHERE price > 100 ORDER BY date DESC LIMIT 10;

SELECT symbol, strategy_id, description FROM stock_analysis JOIN stock_strategies ON stock_analysis.strategy_id = stock_strategies.strategy_id ORDER BY symbol ASC, strategy_id ASC;
